{
  "uid": "v12-4-am-ha",
  "title": "Grafana 12.4 \u2014 HA Alertmanager Metric Rename",
  "description": "12.4 changed the metric name prefix for HA Alertmanager cluster metrics (playbook item #11). This dashboard queries the NEW prefix directly against Grafana's /metrics so you can confirm the rename before pointing your Mimir recording rules / Prometheus alerts at it.",
  "tags": [
    "grafana-12",
    "v12.4",
    "alertmanager",
    "ha",
    "breaking-change",
    "v12-demo"
  ],
  "schemaVersion": 40,
  "version": 1,
  "editable": true,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-30m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {},
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "ds_prom",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "Prometheus",
          "value": "prom"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 10000,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "tags": [
        "demo-guide"
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "html",
        "content": "<div style=\"padding:1.2rem;background:#1a2a3a;border-left:4px solid #5794f2;border-radius:6px;font-family:system-ui\"><div style=\"font-size:.75rem;letter-spacing:.18em;color:#8aa9d0;margin-bottom:.3rem\">DEMO GUIDE</div><div style=\"font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:.6rem\">Grafana 12.4 \u2014 HA Alertmanager Metric Rename</div><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem\"><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#5794f2;margin-bottom:.2rem\">\ud83c\udfaf What you're looking at</div><div style=\"font-size:.88rem;color:#dfe7f0\">v12.4 renamed the HA Alertmanager cluster metric prefix from `alertmanager_cluster_*` to `grafana_alerting_ha_*`. Your Mimir recording rules + SLO dashboards need a sweep.</div></div><div><div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#73bf69;margin-bottom:.2rem\">\ud83e\uddea Try this</div><div style=\"font-size:.88rem;color:#dfe7f0\">Compare the two stats below \u2014 'New prefix' has data, 'Old prefix' shows 0. That's the rename in action.</div></div></div><div style=\"margin-top:.8rem;padding-top:.6rem;border-top:1px solid #2d3e54;font-size:.85rem\">\ud83d\udcda <strong style=\"color:#fff\">Learn more</strong>: <a href=\"https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/alerting/set-up/configure-high-availability/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">Grafana docs</a> \u00b7 <a href=\"https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/whatsnew/whats-new-in-v12-4/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#ff9830\">v12 What's New</a></div></div>"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### HA Alertmanager metric prefix rename (12.4)\n\n| Pre-12.4 | 12.4+ |\n|---|---|\n| `alertmanager_cluster_members` | `grafana_alerting_ha_members` |\n| `alertmanager_cluster_messages_received_total` | `grafana_alerting_ha_messages_received_total` |\n| `alertmanager_cluster_gossip_clock_skew_seconds` | `grafana_alerting_ha_gossip_clock_skew_seconds` |\n\nPanels below query both \u2014 in a fresh 12.4.x instance only the **new** prefix should return data. Use this to verify your Mimir recording rules + Prometheus alerts were migrated."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "New prefix: grafana_alerting_ha_members",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 12
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(grafana_alerting_ha_members) or on() vector(0)"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "description": "New prefix: grafana_alerting_ha_members. Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/alerting/set-up/configure-high-availability/"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "OLD prefix (should be empty): alertmanager_cluster_members",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 7,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 12
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(alertmanager_cluster_members) or on() vector(0)"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "colorMode": "background"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "noValue": "0 \u2014 old prefix retired \u2713"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "description": "OLD prefix (should be empty): alertmanager_cluster_members. Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/alerting/set-up/configure-high-availability/"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Gossip messages \u2014 NEW prefix",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 19
      },
      "datasource": {
        "uid": "${ds_prom}",
        "type": "prometheus"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "rate(grafana_alerting_ha_messages_received_total[$__rate_interval]) or on() vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "received/s"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "rate(grafana_alerting_ha_messages_sent_total[$__rate_interval]) or on() vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "sent/s"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 15
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "displayMode": "table",
          "calcs": [
            "mean",
            "max"
          ]
        }
      },
      "description": "Gossip messages \u2014 NEW prefix. Reference: https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/alerting/set-up/configure-high-availability/"
    }
  ]
}